      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! There isn't a single scratch or smudge to be found, and the interior is still crisp and fresh. It drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as pampered. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
