      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe, a fully overhauled VANOS system, and proactive rod bearing replacement. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the M Variable Differential Lock, providing unparalleled chassis feedback. The factory finish retains its deep luster over a pristine interior with no bolster wear. A turn-key example for the purist demanding peak atmospheric performance and structural integrity.",
