    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2020 Toyota Supra GR is a true collector\u2019s specimen, maintained with obsessive attention to detail. Finished in a stunning Renaissance Red 2.0, the exterior is absolutely flawless, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since day one. There are zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain, let alone a track. Inside, the black Alcantara and leather interior remains in a showroom-fresh state; the seat bolsters show no signs of compression or wear, and the cabin still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the vehicle is perfect. All scheduled maintenance has been performed exclusively at the original dealership, with a comprehensive binder of every service record included. With incredibly low mileage and a completely stock configuration\u2014never modified or tuned\u2014this Supra offers a rare opportunity to own a modern legend in its most pristine, untouched form.",
